unittitle_ssm: Central Baptist Church of Williamsburgh records
abstract_ssm: The Central Baptist Church of Williamsburgh records span the years 1865 to 1910. The collection includes one church register, one volume of membership lists, and two volumes of church minutes. The Central Baptist Church of Williamsburgh was founded in July of 1865 by former members of the First Baptist Church of Williamsburgh.
